---
title: How to set a cry for a Pokémon form?
seoDescription: The way to set a cry for a Pokémon form in Pokémon Studio
publishDate: '2022-09-15 17:30:00'
order: 0
---

As for battle sprites, name the cry according to the format `ID_FORMCry.ogg`.

For example, for Mega Blastoise: `009_30Cry.ogg`.

Then, go to Pokémon Studio, select a Pokémon and its form, then go to the resources tab and set the right cry.

